prisma_schema:
/// The underlying table does not contain a valid unique identifier and can therefore currently not be handled by the Prisma Client.
model contact {
  user          String @default("") @db.VarChar(255)
  contact_type  String @default("Any") @db.VarChar(255)
  contact_value String @default("") @db.VarChar(255)
  update_time   BigInt @default(0) @db.UnsignedBigInt
  id            Int

  @@ignore
}

model order {
  name        String  @default("") @db.VarChar(255)
  start_time  BigInt  @default(0) @db.UnsignedBigInt
  end_time    BigInt  @default(0) @db.UnsignedBigInt
  min_num     Int     @default(1)
  max_num     Int     @default(0)
  creator     String? @db.VarChar(255)
  create_time BigInt  @default(0) @db.UnsignedBigInt
  status      String  @default("Draft") @db.VarChar(255)
  id          Int     @id
}
